# Chamelo Shopify Theme Conventions

## Naming
- Section files: `Index-<feature-name>-new.liquid` (PascalCase feature, kebab-case file)
- CSS classes: `Index_<feature>_<element>_new` (underscore-separated, `_new` suffix)
- CSS files: `index-<feature-name>-new.css` (lowercase kebab)
- Responsive classes: `Desktop_only_new`, `Mobile_only_new`

## Section structure
1. CSS link tag at top: `{{ 'filename.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}`
2. HTML body with `{%- if -%}` blank-checks on all settings
3. Inline `<script>` for Swiper/JS initialization at bottom
4. `{% schema %}` block at end with `name`, `class`, `settings`, `blocks`, `presets`

## CSS patterns
- Use `var(--font-heading-family)` and `var(--font-body-family)` for fonts
- Mobile breakpoint: `@media screen and (max-width: 768px)`
- Use Swiper.js for carousels (already loaded globally)
- Image tags use Shopify's `image_url` + `image_tag` filters with `widths` param

## Important
- Keep `index.json` untouched (live A/B control)
- New landing page work goes in `index.home-v2.json` and its associated sections/assets
